          <h3>Modern Bob</h3>
          <p>Sleek and sophisticated, perfect for any face shape.</p>
          <strong>$45</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="style-card">
        <div class="style-image"><img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.BH7WgMg5JImmNRWX0pexcQHaLH?w=203&h=304&c=7&r=0&o=7&pid=1.7&rm=3" alt="Beachy Waves"></div>
