          <p>Relaxed and effortless, ideal for casual looks.</p>
          <strong>$55</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="style-card">
        <div class="style-image"><img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.3J64qHcLHvEC0WTthTyl9wHaHa?w=203&h=202&c=7&r=0&o=7&pid=1.7&rm=3" alt="Elegant Updo"></div>
