          <h3>Elegant Updo</h3>
          <p>Timeless and classy for special occasions.</p>
          <strong>$65</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="style-card">
        <div class="style-image"><img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.0BCGr08EPxRhMBd-OTwCFAHaHa?w=199&h=199&c=7&r=0&o=7&pid=1.7&rm=3" alt="Undercut Design"></div>
        <div class="style-info">
          <h3>Undercut Design</h3>
          <p>Bold and edgy, express your hair's unique style.</p>
          <strong>$50</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="style-card">
        <div class="style-image"><img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.F7uFbyzryn6ev2Uq6U6EXQHaIH?w=203&h=222&c=7&r=0&o=7&pid=1.7&rm=3" alt="Beach Braids"></div>
        <div class="style-info">
