          <p>A classic and versatile style that's perfect for any occasion.</p>
          <strong>$30</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="style-card">
        <div class="style-image"><img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.IYuHMmXi1rSnEztBG-rzAwHaJ4?w=203&h=270&c=7&r=0&o=7&pid=1.7&rm=3" alt="Royal Crown"></div>
        <div class="style-info">
          <h3>Messy Fringe</h3>
          <p>Chic and carefree, perfect for adding volume and texture.</p>
          <strong>$70</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
